OSCARS version 0.2
===================

DATE: May 12, 2006


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Note that the oscars and topology databases must be set up correctly before
make test will work (more info to be provided).

config.xml in this directory must be copied to $HOME/.oscars.xml, where the
user is the user starting the OSCARS server (more info to be provided).

The MySQL .my.cnf file must exist in the $HOME directory of the user starting
the server.  It must contain the following:

[client]
user=youruser
password=yourpassword

where user is the OSCARS database user, and password is the corrresponding
user.  The default user is named oscars.

